Linux NVM Library

This is src/test/log_open/README.

This directory contains a unit test for pmemlog_open().

The program in log_open.c takes: path

For example:

	./log_open /my/file

This calls pmemlog_open() with the given arguments.

Test cases:

- expected to be successful
	TEST0 existing file
	TEST1 non-existing file

- expected to fail
	TEST2 existing file, but it has read-only permissions

- each case outputs:
	- error, if error happened
	- resulting file size, mode, consistency check results
